Systemd Journal:

journalctl
🛠️ Task 1 – View System Logs
sudo journalctl

Latest 50 entries:

sudo journalctl -n 50

Follow logs live:

sudo journalctl -f

Current boot:

sudo journalctl -b

Previous boot:

sudo journalctl -b -1
